texts.text: >A figure runs across the wasteland with something in its arms.
>It is holding a small demon breathing heavily from a fever.
*Groan*
Hang in there!
Stay with me!
I'll get you through this!
Heh... It's okay... Okay...
Why... The glum face... [sys user_name]?
Yeah... You... Get me through...
>You see what looks to be a town. There might be supplies.
Hmm... Never seen you around here before. You're not from these parts are ya?

!
Is that... a demon you're holding?
Well I'll be damned, a Dx2 traveling alone.
I'm surprised.
You're not surprised?
That I know of Dx2s?

*Chuckle*
Information is important, even in this day and age.
I have to admit though, I've never met one in person before.

*Chuckle*
Nothing surprises me much anymore,
considering the world we live in now.
Besides, I've heard things about humans who can battle demons before.
But enough of that. This demon of yours... It looks to be in bad shape.
Is she your ally?
Sort of.
Something like that.
Yes.
She's burning up from a fever... Things don't look so good if we don't do something about it.
The thing is, we don't got no medical supplies that work on demons here...
She's been poisoned.
Give me some info then.
Poison... There might be something that can help...
Sorry mate, I can't help ya... Wait, maybe...
What is it?
Please, anything that can help.
Oh, it's just a rumor but...
...Okay. Now this is just a rumor okay?
If you go north from here you'll find the ruins of a park.
It's what's left of Ueno Park.
It is said that a unicorn has settled there.
I've heard that a unicorn's horn can cure all poisons,
so maybe that unicorn's horn can do the job...
The thing is, that unicorn is vicious and will attack anything that steps foot inside.
You're safe as long as you're outside cuz it never leaves the grounds,
but no one who entered has ever returned.
>You sit by a crackling campfire.
>You are inside what was once called Ueno Park,
>waiting for the unicorn to show up. But there's no sign of it at all.
>You look into the dancing flames as if in a trance.
>--X years ago--
>You are climbing aimlessly up some unknown mountain path.
>The world was devastated by the rain of ICBMs and the infighting among frenzied humans.
>Human population dropped drastically, and demons were everywhere.
>You were unable to stop the worst of the worst from happening.
>You foresee the end of all mankind coming soon in the near future.
Grrrr...
*Growl*
Draw your sword.
Brace for the attack.
*Howl*
*Bark*
>You sidestep the demon's attack and slash its front leg.
*Growl*
>After a brief standoff, the demon runs off.
>Sheathing your sword, you continue up the mountain path.
>All this power, and still you were able to save no one.
>...Tired of thinking, you just want to clear your mind.
>Climbing blindly up, you come to the end of the mountain path.
>Before you is a cliff so deep that to fall would mean certain death...
Walk towards the edge.
Dive off the cliff.
>You take a step towards the edge, dislodging some pebbles by your feet and sending them tumbling down the abyss.
>There are no more friends to talk you out of jumping now, so you think might as well...
*Groan*
>You hear a groaning sound, so faint that it is barely audible through the wind.
*Groan*
>Just a few steps away lies a tiny little demon.
>She seems to be alive, though her vitals are faint.
>--Present day--
>A nearby sound snaps your mind back to the present, and you turn around hastily with sword in hand.
>You see an especially big unicorn looking at you.

*Neigh*
Human... Human, human...!
